WEBVTT

00:14.482 --> 00:16.084
I'll make it up to you.

00:16.084 --> 00:17.552
I've got a hook up
with a guy

00:17.552 --> 00:20.454
who'll get us a table
at Mozza.

00:20.454 --> 00:21.856
I'll call you tonight, baby.

00:25.326 --> 00:28.129
Please, baby.
I know a guy.

00:28.129 --> 00:29.463
Remember to get us
a gas card,

00:29.463 --> 00:30.699
or you too busy
making plans

00:30.699 --> 00:32.366
to get your ashes hauled
when you get back?

00:32.366 --> 00:34.035
See, Harry,
if you wasn't such a
fuckin' monk,

00:34.035 --> 00:35.570
you'd know what it's
like out there.

00:35.570 --> 00:38.907
It takes a lot of
maintenance. Yes,
I got the gas card.

00:38.907 --> 00:41.475
Then let's get goin' or
we're crossin' the desert
at high noon.

00:42.577 --> 00:45.614
Hold up.
Bosch.

00:45.614 --> 00:47.281
When?

00:47.281 --> 00:49.317
Send him back.

00:49.317 --> 00:52.086
- Nash.
- Wants to tell us
he solved the case?

00:52.086 --> 00:53.054
Hm.

00:55.056 --> 00:57.859
Carl.

00:57.859 --> 00:59.160
Wish you'd called.

00:59.160 --> 01:01.029
Gettin' ready to
hit the road for Vegas.

01:01.029 --> 01:02.631
- Picking up your guy?
- The extradition hearing's

01:02.631 --> 01:03.832
first thing
tomorrow morning.

01:03.832 --> 01:05.299
Yeah, that's sort of
why I came in

01:05.299 --> 01:07.335
- if you've got a minute.
- A minute, sure.

01:07.335 --> 01:08.302
Yeah.
Someplace private?

01:12.540 --> 01:15.276
Grab a seat.

01:15.276 --> 01:17.145
Yeah, the other day...

01:17.145 --> 01:22.350
when you were asking me
about Tony Allen--

01:22.350 --> 01:23.351
Yeah.

01:25.186 --> 01:27.388
What's on your mind?
What'd you leave out?

01:27.388 --> 01:31.192
Okay. About six months ago
I'm doing my rounds.

01:31.192 --> 01:33.662
It's a nice evening,
windows down,

01:33.662 --> 01:35.697
I roll past
the Allen's house,

01:35.697 --> 01:37.265
I hear voices.

01:37.265 --> 01:40.534
An argument. Two men,
sounds like it could
get out of hand.

01:40.534 --> 01:42.170
So you thought you'd
check it out.

01:42.170 --> 01:46.040
Yeah. So I park.
I walk down the side of
the Allen's house,

01:46.040 --> 01:47.976
Allen and this other guy
are in--

01:47.976 --> 01:51.445
looks like a home office,
goin' at it.

01:51.445 --> 01:52.546
What about?
Could you tell?

01:52.546 --> 01:54.248
Money.

01:54.248 --> 01:56.417
The other guy's like,
"Where's my money, Tone?"

01:56.417 --> 01:57.719
over and over,
and Allen's like,

01:57.719 --> 01:59.520
"Oh, I wouldn't
do that to ya, I swear."

01:59.520 --> 02:01.222
Other guy,
he sign in at the gate?

02:01.222 --> 02:05.593
I checked the log.
There were no visitors for
the Allens that night.

02:05.593 --> 02:07.195
So he must have
come in with Tony.

02:07.195 --> 02:10.298
So why are you
tellin' me this now?

02:10.298 --> 02:12.500
You said there'd been
an arrest in Vegas.

02:12.500 --> 02:16.504
I was-- started thinkin',
yeah, we talked about
made guys, mob guys.

02:16.504 --> 02:20.241
I just remembered this guy
Allen had the fight with.

02:20.241 --> 02:22.476
I mean, he had that vibe,
the, you know--

02:22.476 --> 02:24.779
- Vegas wise guy.
- Absolutely, definitely.

02:24.779 --> 02:26.347
Mobster all the way.

02:26.347 --> 02:29.217
Think you could
pick him out of a six pack?

02:29.217 --> 02:31.419
Yeah, I think I could.

02:31.419 --> 02:32.386
Follow me.

02:34.723 --> 02:36.725
Nah.
It's none of these guys.

02:36.725 --> 02:38.092
- You sure?
- Yeah.

02:39.994 --> 02:42.530
That's the guy.
That's the guy!

02:42.530 --> 02:43.564
You sure about that?

02:43.564 --> 02:45.499
No doubt.

02:45.499 --> 02:47.201
Okay, we'll check it out.

02:47.201 --> 02:48.837
- Really appreciate it, Carl.
- Thanks.

02:48.837 --> 02:51.105
Am I-- Am I right?
He's a made guy?

02:51.105 --> 02:54.375
We talk to him,
we'll ask him about that.

02:54.375 --> 02:58.246
Okay.
I-- I should shove off.

02:58.246 --> 03:00.749
- Uh, good luck in Vegas.
- Thanks.

03:00.749 --> 03:01.950
- Yeah.
- Thanks for coming in.

03:01.950 --> 03:03.184
Yeah, safe travel.

03:11.292 --> 03:12.360
Joey Marks.

