We got time for this?

04:24.899 --> 04:26.567
Check in's not 'til 3:00.

04:26.567 --> 04:27.568
Is it worth it?
We got Rykoff.

04:27.568 --> 04:28.837
On a platter.

04:28.837 --> 04:31.705
Your Christmas pig.
Courtesy of the FBI.

04:31.705 --> 04:34.142
Feds got it all worked out.

04:34.142 --> 04:35.509
