04:37.478 --> 04:39.848
And that will give them
something on their
counter terrorism thing.

04:39.848 --> 04:42.550
- Exactly.
- Still want to find
this Layla,

04:42.550 --> 04:44.418
ask her what she knows.

04:44.418 --> 04:46.154
Yeah, this is all
residential.

04:46.154 --> 04:48.923
Yeah, and Tony wrote it off
on his taxes as an office.

04:48.923 --> 04:51.125
I dig this.
What is this?

04:51.125 --> 04:52.861
Sonny Rollins
and Miles Davis

04:52.861 --> 04:54.362
on Miles' album
"Bag's Groove."

04:54.362 --> 04:56.764
Sweet.
What's it called?

04:56.764 --> 04:59.333
"Doxy."
Sonny wrote it.

04:59.333 --> 05:01.402
- You know a lot
about this stuff.
- A little.

05:01.402 --> 05:03.171
Ever listen to anything
written in this century?

05:03.171 --> 05:04.939
Still catching up on
the last one.

05:04.939 --> 05:06.407
Pull over, this is it.

05:06.407 --> 05:09.343
